description: Sticky, sweet and moreish chicken! This buffalo wings recipe with fresh peach and a kick of cayenne will have your family begging for more!
name: Peach Buffalo Wings Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 800 g Macro free range wing nibbles

recipeInstructions.text: Dip chicken, one at a time, in peach mixture to lightly coat, then return to tray. Bake for 25 minutes, turning halfway, or until chicken is cooked through. Brush chicken with reserved peach mixture, then bake for a further 10 minutes or until golden and sticky. Serve with celery and ranch dressing.
